snippet.title: Gun World VR Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
GunWorld VR is a gun sandbox / shooting range game for VR, released in Early Access on the Steam Store and Oculus Quest. You can purchase game on Oculus: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4307257289362025/

Oculus: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4307257289362025/
Sidequest: https://sidequestvr.com/app/5220
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1585530/GunWorld_VR
Discord: https://discord.gg/zdX9PCt





Music: 'Legionnaire'  by Scott Buckley
